      • create

        public SourceTreeWithCodeCachingPreparationProcessor create()
        Crates a new instance of the SourceTreeWithCodeCachingPreparationProcessor. If you do not set some specific implementations explicitly, then the following default ones are used:
        • SourceAlwaysExpiredChecker
        • LessImportResolverImpl
        • LessImportReplacerImpl
        • SourceFactory created by SourceFactoryBuilder with standard factories ( SourceFactoryBuilder.withStandard())
        Returns:
        the new instance of the SourceTreeWithCodeCachingPreparationProcessor.
        Since:
        1.0
